<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٨٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>كَمْ لَبِثَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> بِمَكَّةَ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> عَشْرًا.<span class="c5"> قُلْتُ:</span> فَإِنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنَ عَبَّاسٍ </a>يَقُولُ: بِضْعَ عَشْرَةَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> فَغَفَّرَهُ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> إِنَّمَا أَخَذَهُ مِنْ قَوْلِ الشَّاعِرِ .»<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>